Package: bartext
Type: Package
Title: A ggplot2 geom that displays labeled items in a bar chart
Version: 0.0.9000
Author: Eric Hare
Maintainer: Eric Hare <eric@omnianalytics.io>
Description: Implements a geom which extends both geom_text() and geom_bar()
    to draw labels for a particular column inside each bar. This geom is best
    suited for smaller datasets in which the elements that comprise a particular
    bar are of interest to the user or developer.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    grid,
    rlang
Collate: 
    'geom_bartext.R'
